293
00:20:58.090 --> 00:21:00.710
That was beneath me. Your Grace.

294
00:20:58.090 --> 00:21:00.710
I apologize.

295
00:21:03.890 --> 00:21:05.690
I have to believe.

296
00:21:05.760 --> 00:21:09.390
that in the end.

297
00:21:05.760 --> 00:21:09.390
honor and decency will prevail.

298
00:21:10.460 --> 00:21:13.700
We need to hew to that

299
00:21:10.460 --> 00:21:13.700
and to each other.

300
00:21:32.590 --> 00:21:33.750
Whose idea was it?

301
00:21:39.260 --> 00:21:40.820
The pig.

302
00:21:40.930 --> 00:21:43.560
- Was it your plot?

303
00:21:40.930 --> 00:21:43.560
No...

304
00:21:44.170 --> 00:21:47.160
It was Jace and...

305
00:21:48.470 --> 00:21:50.600
it was the two of them.

306
00:21:50.670 --> 00:21:52.000
I couldn't be sure.

307
00:21:52.110 --> 00:21:53.510
Aemond is your brother.

308
00:21:53.610 --> 00:21:55.740
- Well. he's a twat.

309
00:21:53.610 --> 00:21:55.740
We are family.

310
00:21:55.810 --> 00:21:58.140
You may cuff him about

311
00:21:55.810 --> 00:21:58.140
as you wish at home.

312
00:21:58.250 --> 00:22:01.340
but in the world.

313
00:21:58.250 --> 00:22:01.340
we must defend our own.

314
00:22:01.450 --> 00:22:02.510
It was funny.

315
00:22:02.620 --> 00:22:05.450
Do you think Rhaenyra's sons

316
00:22:02.620 --> 00:22:05.450
will be your playthings forever?

317
00:22:07.190 --> 00:22:08.180
As things stand...

318
00:22:09.290 --> 00:22:12.920
Rhaenyra will ascend the throne

319
00:22:09.290 --> 00:22:12.920
and Jacaerys Targaryen will be her heir.

320
00:22:13.490 --> 00:22:16.090
- So?

321
00:22:13.490 --> 00:22:16.090
You are nearly a man-grown.

322
00:22:16.160 --> 00:22:18.260
How is it that

323
00:22:16.160 --> 00:22:18.260
you can be so shortsighted?

324
00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:22.990
If Rhaenyra comes into power...

325
00:22:23.640 --> 00:22:26.270
your very life could be forfeit.

326
00:22:27.340 --> 00:22:28.780
Aemond's as well.

327
00:22:29.780 --> 00:22:32.650
She could move to cut off any challenge

328
00:22:29.780 --> 00:22:32.650
to her succession.

329
00:22:33.380 --> 00:22:35.180
- Then I won't challenge--

330
00:22:33.380 --> 00:22:35.180
- You are the challenge!

331
00:22:35.280 --> 00:22:36.770
You are the challenge. Aegon!

332
00:22:36.850 --> 00:22:39.480
Simply by living and breathing!

333
00:22:43.890 --> 00:22:46.860
You are the King's firstborn son

334
00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:49.730
and what they know.

335
00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:49.730
what everyone in the realm knows

336
00:22:49.830 --> 00:22:51.820
in their blood and in their bones...

337
00:22:53.000 --> 00:22:55.990
is that one day. you will be our King.

338
00:23:04.910 --> 00:23:05.970
Get dressed.

339
00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:03.300
Dracarys!

340
00:24:31.130 --> 00:24:33.570
The lamb hearts are excellent.

341
00:24:33.630 --> 00:24:36.400
We are fortunate in our cook.

342
00:24:33.630 --> 00:24:36.400
Your Excellence.

343
00:24:36.470 --> 00:24:37.800
There's a plum-cake

344
00:24:36.470 --> 00:24:37.800
yet to be served.

345
00:24:37.910 --> 00:24:39.430
which will have us

346
00:24:37.910 --> 00:24:39.430
fighting over the crumbs.

347
00:24:39.910 --> 00:24:41.900
Then before we come to blows...

348
00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:47.310
a toast to Aegon the Conqueror.

349
00:24:43.440 --> 00:24:47.310
your exalted forebear.

350
00:24:47.410 --> 00:24:50.980
who joined our cause against Volantis

351
00:24:47.410 --> 00:24:50.980
in the Century of Blood.

352
00:24:51.090 --> 00:24:54.610
On the great dragon Balerion.

353
00:24:51.090 --> 00:24:54.610
he flew to our aid in Lys

354
00:24:54.690 --> 00:24:58.280
and burned a fleet of enemy ships.

355
00:24:54.690 --> 00:24:58.280
thus turning the tide.

356
00:25:00.490 --> 00:25:03.120
- Aegon the Conqueror.

357
00:25:00.490 --> 00:25:03.120
To Aegon.

358
00:25:06.330 --> 00:25:08.000
This brings me to some business.

359
00:25:08.970 --> 00:25:11.130
A proposal I wish to make

360
00:25:11.210 --> 00:25:14.140
in the spirit of honoring

361
00:25:11.210 --> 00:25:14.140
our storied alliance.

362
00:25:14.210 --> 00:25:16.680
If your aim is to marry

363
00:25:14.210 --> 00:25:16.680
one of our daughters. Your Excellence.

364
00:25:16.780 --> 00:25:18.800
you might have said so

365
00:25:16.780 --> 00:25:18.800
and spared us the history lesson.

366
00:25:18.880 --> 00:25:20.140
- What?

367
00:25:21.180 --> 00:25:24.350
I would not count myself

368
00:25:21.180 --> 00:25:24.350
so deserving. my lady Laena.

369
00:25:26.990 --> 00:25:31.360
I wish to offer you

370
00:25:26.990 --> 00:25:31.360
a permanent residence here in Pentos.

371
00:25:31.460 --> 00:25:33.860
This manse I would gift

372
00:25:31.460 --> 00:25:33.860
to you. outright.

373
00:25:33.960 --> 00:25:36.230
along with its farms and lands.

374
00:25:36.330 --> 00:25:38.030
the vineyard and the wood.

375
00:25:38.130 --> 00:25:40.230
The tenants would pay

376
00:25:38.130 --> 00:25:40.230
their tributes annually

377
00:25:40.330 --> 00:25:42.200
to their new Targaryen lord.

378
00:25:42.300 --> 00:25:45.030
You would have your freedom

379
00:25:42.300 --> 00:25:45.030
of the city and the harbor.

380
00:25:45.140 --> 00:25:47.900
as befits your royal station.

381
00:25:51.080 --> 00:25:52.480
Continue.

382
00:25:52.550 --> 00:25:55.850
Lys and its allies rise again.

383
00:25:55.920 --> 00:26:00.050
The Triarchy has made common cause

384
00:25:55.920 --> 00:26:00.050
with Qoren Martell of Dorne.

385
00:26:00.550 --> 00:26:03.580
At any moment.

386
00:26:00.550 --> 00:26:03.580
they may turn their sights north.

387
00:26:03.690 --> 00:26:06.090
Your family has dragons.

388
00:26:06.190 --> 00:26:10.030
Three now. mayhaps four in the future.

389
00:26:11.030 --> 00:26:14.870
My aim is to protect Pentos

390
00:26:11.030 --> 00:26:14.870
from the lustful eye of the Triarchy.

391
00:26:14.940 --> 00:26:18.670
Aid Pentos in this. as Aegon once did...

392
00:26:19.270 --> 00:26:23.440
and my gratitude will fill your cup

393
00:26:19.270 --> 00:26:23.440
and overflow it.

394
00:26:23.540 --> 00:26:25.840
Your Excellence. we are travelers.

395
00:26:25.910 --> 00:26:28.540
We've already extended our visit here.

396
00:26:32.920 --> 00:26:34.720
It's a most generous offer.

397
00:26:35.390 --> 00:26:37.380
And one we will certainly entertain.

398
00:27:07.890 --> 00:27:10.410
You are considering

399
00:27:07.890 --> 00:27:10.410
Prince Reggio's offer.

400
00:27:10.490 --> 00:27:12.480
We have a good life here.

401
00:27:12.590 --> 00:27:15.890
We're free to do as we please.

402
00:27:12.590 --> 00:27:15.890
welcomed and feted.

403
00:27:15.960 --> 00:27:18.400
- And eternally guests.

404
00:27:15.960 --> 00:27:18.400
- Precisely.

405
00:27:18.470 --> 00:27:21.440
We are without responsibility.

406
00:27:18.470 --> 00:27:21.440
The political scheming.

407
00:27:21.500 --> 00:27:24.170
the endless shifting

408
00:27:21.500 --> 00:27:24.170
of loyalties and succession

409
00:27:24.270 --> 00:27:25.760
is none of ours.

410
00:27:26.510 --> 00:27:29.500
- They are using us.

411
00:27:26.510 --> 00:27:29.500
- It's refreshing. isn't it?

412
00:27:30.980 --> 00:27:32.670
A simple transaction.

413
00:27:32.780 --> 00:27:35.270
We have dragons. they have gold.

414
00:27:40.490 --> 00:27:42.350
We are more than this. Daemon.

415
00:27:42.460 --> 00:27:43.790
We are not minstrels or mummers

416
00:27:43.860 --> 00:27:45.450
who play at the pleasure

417
00:27:43.860 --> 00:27:45.450
of an alien prince.

418
00:27:45.530 --> 00:27:47.960
We are the blood of Old Valyria.

419
00:27:48.960 --> 00:27:50.290
We don't belong here.

420
00:27:50.360 --> 00:27:52.800
Valyria is gone.

421
00:27:50.360 --> 00:27:52.800
We don't belong anywhere.

422
00:27:58.940 --> 00:28:03.500
I want my child to be born

423
00:27:58.940 --> 00:28:03.500
where I was born. on Driftmark.

424
00:28:03.610 --> 00:28:04.770
in my lord father's castle.

425
00:28:04.850 --> 00:28:07.540
I want my daughters to be

426
00:28:04.850 --> 00:28:07.540
raised in their homeland

427
00:28:07.650 --> 00:28:11.640
with their family

428
00:28:07.650 --> 00:28:11.640
according to their birthright.

429
00:28:13.790 --> 00:28:17.220
And at my end. I want to die

430
00:28:13.790 --> 00:28:17.220
a dragonrider's death.

431
00:28:17.320 --> 00:28:19.950
Not that of some fat country lord.

432
00:28:52.930 --> 00:28:55.090
- Soften your knees.

433
00:28:55.200 --> 00:28:56.190
Feet light.

434
00:28:57.600 --> 00:28:59.260
Keep your feet light

435
00:28:57.600 --> 00:28:59.260
and your hands heavy.

436
00:28:59.370 --> 00:29:01.890
This is the stuff. Lyonel.

437
00:29:02.000 --> 00:29:05.400
Lads that learn together.

438
00:29:02.000 --> 00:29:05.400
train together...

439
00:29:05.510 --> 00:29:08.370
knock each other down.

440
00:29:05.510 --> 00:29:08.370
pick each other up.

441
00:29:08.440 --> 00:29:11.210
They will certainly form

442
00:29:08.440 --> 00:29:11.210
a lifelong bond. wouldn't you agree?

443
00:29:11.950 --> 00:29:13.410
That is the hope. Your Grace.

444
00:29:16.280 --> 00:29:18.880
Don't stand too upright. my prince.

445
00:29:16.280 --> 00:29:18.880
You'll get knocked down.

446
00:29:30.060 --> 00:29:31.050
Aegon.

447
00:29:32.870 --> 00:29:34.560
I've won my first bout.

448
00:29:32.870 --> 00:29:34.560
Ser Criston.

449
00:29:34.640 --> 00:29:37.070
My opponent sues for mercy.

450
00:29:37.600 --> 00:29:40.730
You'll have a new opponent then.

451
00:29:37.600 --> 00:29:40.730
my Lord of the Straw.

452
00:29:40.810 --> 00:29:42.400
Let's see if you can touch me.

453
00:29:43.380 --> 00:29:44.780
You and your brother.

454
00:30:12.340 --> 00:30:13.970
You're gonna have

455
00:30:12.340 --> 00:30:13.970
to do better than that.

456
00:30:18.450 --> 00:30:19.610
Ah!

457
00:30:19.680 --> 00:30:20.670
Weapons up. boys.

458
00:30:21.280 --> 00:30:22.910
Give your enemies no quarter.

459
00:30:25.250 --> 00:30:26.950
It seems the younger boys

460
00:30:25.250 --> 00:30:26.950
could do better

461
00:30:27.020 --> 00:30:30.320
with a bit of your attention.

462
00:30:27.020 --> 00:30:30.320
Ser Criston.

463
00:30:30.420 --> 00:30:33.330
You question my method

464
00:30:30.420 --> 00:30:33.330
of instruction. ser?

465
00:30:33.430 --> 00:30:36.860
Oh. I merely suggest that

466
00:30:33.430 --> 00:30:36.860
method be applied to all your pupils.

467
00:30:40.600 --> 00:30:41.590
Very well.

468
00:30:45.170 --> 00:30:47.160
- Jacaerys. come here.

469
00:30:47.270 --> 00:30:48.470
You spar with Aegon.

470
00:30:51.680 --> 00:30:53.110
Eldest son against eldest son.

471
00:30:56.350 --> 00:30:57.680
It's hardly a fair match.

472
00:30:57.780 --> 00:30:59.950
I know you've never seen true battle.

473
00:30:57.780 --> 00:30:59.950
ser. but when steel is drawn.

474
00:31:00.020 --> 00:31:01.960
a fair match isn't something

475
00:31:00.020 --> 00:31:01.960
anyone should expect.

476
00:31:04.730 --> 00:31:05.950
Blades up.

477
00:31:07.190 --> 00:31:08.290
- Engage.

478
00:31:14.200 --> 00:31:15.170
Ah!

479
00:31:32.690 --> 00:31:34.150
- Foul play.

480
00:31:32.690 --> 00:31:34.150
- I'll deal with him.

481
00:31:37.220 --> 00:31:39.060
Plant your feet.

482
00:31:37.220 --> 00:31:39.060
You have a height advantage.

483
00:31:39.160 --> 00:31:41.920
Use it. Advance on him...

484
00:31:46.330 --> 00:31:47.430
You!

485
00:31:48.940 --> 00:31:50.100
Close with him.

486
00:31:51.000 --> 00:31:53.240
Press him backward!

487
00:31:51.000 --> 00:31:53.240
Close with him!

488
00:31:53.740 --> 00:31:55.730
Stay on the attack! Use your feet!

489
00:31:59.080 --> 00:32:00.070
Don't let him get up.

490
00:32:02.680 --> 00:32:03.910
Stay on the attack!

491
00:32:05.290 --> 00:32:06.510
Enough!

492
00:32:08.260 --> 00:32:10.880
You dare put hands on me?

493
00:32:08.260 --> 00:32:10.880
- Aegon!

494
00:32:10.960 --> 00:32:12.860
You forget yourself. Strong.

495
00:32:10.960 --> 00:32:12.860
That is the Prince.

496
00:32:12.930 --> 00:32:14.550
This is what you teach. Cole?

497
00:32:17.100 --> 00:32:18.290
Cruelty...

498
00:32:19.300 --> 00:32:20.460
to the weaker opponent?

499
00:32:23.470 --> 00:32:25.200
Your interest

500
00:32:23.470 --> 00:32:25.200
in the princeling's training

501
00:32:25.270 --> 00:32:26.710
is quite unusual. Commander.

502
00:32:28.980 --> 00:32:30.810
Most men would only

503
00:32:28.980 --> 00:32:30.810
have that kind of devotion

504
00:32:30.910 --> 00:32:32.310
toward a cousin...

505
00:32:34.080 --> 00:32:35.070
or a brother...

506
00:32:36.150 --> 00:32:37.140
or a son.

507
00:32:53.800 --> 00:32:55.430
Get back!

508
00:32:55.970 --> 00:32:57.440
Say it again!

509
00:32:58.270 --> 00:32:59.670
Say it again!

510
00:32:59.770 --> 00:33:01.500
Thought as much.

511
00:33:04.980 --> 00:33:06.570
Let him be bathed

512
00:33:04.980 --> 00:33:06.570
with a cloth.

513
00:33:06.650 --> 00:33:08.240
and see to it the cook

514
00:33:08.320 --> 00:33:10.310
gives you a good. clear wine to drink.

515
00:33:12.820 --> 00:33:13.910
Princess...

516
00:33:14.750 --> 00:33:17.950
there's been an incident in the yard.

517
00:33:27.330 --> 00:33:29.600
It fills me

518
00:33:27.330 --> 00:33:29.600
with unrelenting shame.

519
00:33:29.670 --> 00:33:32.000
So that's what

520
00:33:29.670 --> 00:33:32.000
this is about then?

521
00:33:32.110 --> 00:33:34.700
- Your shame?

522
00:33:32.110 --> 00:33:34.700
Our shame. Harwin!

523
00:33:35.680 --> 00:33:37.200
Shame on the whole of House Strong.

524
00:33:37.310 --> 00:33:40.180
Because I laid my hands

525
00:33:37.310 --> 00:33:40.180
on that insufferable Cole.

526
00:33:40.280 --> 00:33:41.180
the son of a steward?

527
00:33:41.280 --> 00:33:42.650
He is a Knight

528
00:33:41.280 --> 00:33:42.650
of the Kingsguard now.

529
00:33:42.720 --> 00:33:44.550
- a defender of the crown.

530
00:33:42.720 --> 00:33:44.550
He assailed Prince Jacaerys.

531
00:33:44.650 --> 00:33:46.480
the future heir to the throne.

532
00:33:48.520 --> 00:33:52.690
You have laid us open to accusations

533
00:33:52.790 --> 00:33:54.520
of an uglier treachery.

534
00:33:54.630 --> 00:33:56.790
And what treachery is that?

535
00:33:59.300 --> 00:34:01.500
Don't play the fool with me. boy.

536
00:34:03.040 --> 00:34:06.200
Your intimacy with the Princess Rhaenyra

537
00:34:06.310 --> 00:34:09.240
is an offense that would

538
00:34:06.310 --> 00:34:09.240
mean exile and death...

539
00:34:09.810 --> 00:34:13.410
for you. for her. for the children!

540
00:34:14.510 --> 00:34:16.680
It is rumor only...

541
00:34:18.820 --> 00:34:20.180
spun by the Princess's rivals.

542
00:34:20.250 --> 00:34:21.850
People have eyes. boy.

543
00:34:24.720 --> 00:34:29.030
Yet His Grace the King. it seems.

544
00:34:24.720 --> 00:34:29.030
will not accept what his eyes see.

545
00:34:29.100 --> 00:34:33.690
This flimsy shield alone

546
00:34:29.100 --> 00:34:33.690
stands between you and the headsman.

547
00:34:34.830 --> 00:34:37.860
The willful blindness of a father

548
00:34:34.830 --> 00:34:37.860
towards his child.

549
00:34:37.940 --> 00:34:40.410
I wish my father affected

550
00:34:37.940 --> 00:34:40.410
a similar blindness.

551
00:34:40.510 --> 00:34:42.770
Have I not these many years?

552
00:34:43.410 --> 00:34:45.570
And yet today. you publicly assaulted

553
00:34:45.680 --> 00:34:48.670
a knight of the Kingsguard

554
00:34:45.680 --> 00:34:48.670
in the... in the defense of your--

555
00:34:51.520 --> 00:34:54.720
You have your honor

556
00:34:51.520 --> 00:34:54.720
and I have mine.

557
00:35:02.860 --> 00:35:04.850
To ease the pain. Princess.

558
00:35:17.240 --> 00:35:19.910
- Thank you.

559
00:35:17.240 --> 00:35:19.910
- You'll feel better in a day or two.

560
00:35:19.980 --> 00:35:21.610
when the milk dries up.

561
00:35:40.230 --> 00:35:42.230
- My dear wife.

562
00:35:42.300 --> 00:35:44.130
Princess.

563
00:35:44.240 --> 00:35:45.140
Oh.

564
00:35:45.970 --> 00:35:47.170
I fell down.

565
00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:51.600
- Where have you been?

566
00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:51.600
Out with Qarl.

567
00:35:51.680 --> 00:35:52.510
Didn't I mention it?

568
00:35:54.580 --> 00:35:56.850
Are you in very much pain?

569
00:35:56.950 --> 00:35:57.940
The milk...

570
00:35:59.190 --> 00:36:01.450
- swells the breasts--

571
00:35:59.190 --> 00:36:01.450
- Would you mind. Ser Qarl?

572
00:36:01.520 --> 00:36:03.110
I would like to speak with my husband.

573
00:36:03.190 --> 00:36:04.920
Of course. Princess.

574
00:36:16.370 --> 00:36:20.500
War is afoot again

575
00:36:16.370 --> 00:36:20.500
in the Stepstones. Rhaenyra.

576
00:36:21.340 --> 00:36:25.800
The Triarchy takes new life

577
00:36:21.340 --> 00:36:25.800
from its alliance with Dorne.

578
00:36:26.880 --> 00:36:28.870
They're waylaying ships and cargo.

579
00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:32.180
Qarl's been fighting there.

580
00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:32.180
He showed me a--

581
00:36:35.460 --> 00:36:39.220
He showed me a sack of sapphires

582
00:36:35.460 --> 00:36:39.220
big as walnuts

583
