- If you insist. my king.

872
00:50:21.810 --> 00:50:24.440
- I do.

873
00:50:25.350 --> 00:50:27.380
You will continue in your service

874
00:50:25.350 --> 00:50:27.380
to the Crown.

875
00:50:30.060 --> 00:50:32.120
I would then ask leave

876
00:50:30.060 --> 00:50:32.120
to take my son from court

877
00:50:32.190 --> 00:50:35.290
and escort him back to the family seat

878
00:50:32.190 --> 00:50:35.290
at Harrenhal.

879
00:50:35.360 --> 00:50:37.350
He is my heir

880
00:50:37.460 --> 00:50:39.230
and will be lord of Harren's castle

881
00:50:37.460 --> 00:50:39.230
one day.

882
00:50:39.330 --> 00:50:41.960
It is time he assumed his duties there.

883
00:50:45.040 --> 00:50:46.130
Do it.

884
00:51:06.930 --> 00:51:08.920
Aren't you gonna help me?

885
00:51:48.400 --> 00:51:51.230
I took the liberty of beginning

886
00:51:48.400 --> 00:51:51.230
without you. Your Grace.

887
00:51:51.300 --> 00:51:54.070
It seemed a sin to let

888
00:51:51.300 --> 00:51:54.070
such a pie grow cold.

889
00:51:54.140 --> 00:51:57.040
You did wisely. Lord Larys.

890
00:51:57.110 --> 00:51:59.940
Though you had no such worry

891
00:51:57.110 --> 00:51:59.940
about the wine. surely.

892
00:52:00.050 --> 00:52:02.640
Meat without wine is also a sin.

893
00:52:02.750 --> 00:52:03.980
Hmm.

894
00:52:08.290 --> 00:52:10.920
It's been my duty to tell you

895
00:52:08.290 --> 00:52:10.920
of happenings about the castle.

896
00:52:10.990 --> 00:52:13.980
but tonight you know. and I do not.

897
00:52:14.890 --> 00:52:17.620
The King had an audience with my father.

898
00:52:17.730 --> 00:52:19.260
He attempted to resign his post.

899
00:52:20.330 --> 00:52:21.460
I thought as much.

900
00:52:22.940 --> 00:52:26.570
His honor's always been a millstone

901
00:52:22.940 --> 00:52:26.570
about his esteemed neck.

902
00:52:28.740 --> 00:52:30.680
Interesting you said "attempted"?

903
00:52:30.780 --> 00:52:32.770
My lord husband refused to accept.

904
00:52:34.010 --> 00:52:37.970
Then he fell short of confessing

905
00:52:34.010 --> 00:52:37.970
my brother's... transgressions.

906
00:52:38.080 --> 00:52:40.280
With his eruption in the yard.

907
00:52:38.080 --> 00:52:40.280
your brother

908
00:52:40.350 --> 00:52:42.480
all but confessed the truth himself.

909
00:52:42.590 --> 00:52:44.780
Truth has many flavors. Your Grace.

910
00:52:45.860 --> 00:52:48.520
Do you expect the King to doom

911
00:52:45.860 --> 00:52:48.520
his dear daughter to exile.

912
00:52:48.630 --> 00:52:50.460
- or even--

913
00:52:52.030 --> 00:52:53.260
Talya. not now.

914
00:53:00.540 --> 00:53:04.140
It's a willful blindness. the King.

915
00:53:04.210 --> 00:53:05.870
I mean. you'd surely

916
00:53:04.210 --> 00:53:05.870
suffer the same affliction.

917
00:53:05.980 --> 00:53:07.880
- if it came to it.

918
00:53:05.980 --> 00:53:07.880
- I would not.

919
00:53:09.720 --> 00:53:12.620
Lord Lyonel is to escort

920
00:53:09.720 --> 00:53:12.620
Ser Harwin back to Harrenhal

921
00:53:12.690 --> 00:53:16.120
to watch over his seat

922
00:53:12.690 --> 00:53:16.120
whilst he continues to serve as Hand.

923
00:53:16.690 --> 00:53:21.390
But the Hand is compromised

924
00:53:16.690 --> 00:53:21.390
by the acts of his son.

925
00:53:21.490 --> 00:53:26.450
My father cannot give

926
00:53:21.490 --> 00:53:26.450
unbiased counsel to the King.

927
00:53:26.530 --> 00:53:29.830
It is now that I most rue

928
00:53:26.530 --> 00:53:29.830
the absence of my own father.

929
00:53:29.900 --> 00:53:31.800
He wouldn't hesitate

930
00:53:29.900 --> 00:53:31.800
to speak the truth to the King.

931
00:53:31.870 --> 00:53:33.400
If Otto Hightower were still Hand--

932
00:53:33.510 --> 00:53:35.910
You cannot say. my queen.

933
00:53:33.510 --> 00:53:35.910
that your father would be

934
00:53:36.010 --> 00:53:37.530
impartial in this matter.

935
00:53:37.640 --> 00:53:39.840
No. but he would be partial to me!

936
00:53:49.250 --> 00:53:52.250
In all of King's Landing.

937
00:53:49.250 --> 00:53:52.250
is there no one to take my side?

938
00:54:18.420 --> 00:54:21.620
What a collection of heroes

939
00:54:18.420 --> 00:54:21.620
I have before me.

940
00:54:25.590 --> 00:54:27.360
A murderer...

941
00:54:27.930 --> 00:54:30.020
a deviant...

942
00:54:30.530 --> 00:54:32.520
a traitor to the Crown.

943
00:54:33.230 --> 00:54:37.430
For your crimes. you've been sentenced

944
00:54:33.230 --> 00:54:37.430
to death by hanging.

945
00:54:39.370 --> 00:54:41.360
What do you want with us?

946
00:54:44.540 --> 00:54:47.540
I am prepared to offer you mercy...

947
00:54:49.150 --> 00:54:52.140
if you're prepared

948
00:54:49.150 --> 00:54:52.140
to pay a little price.

949
00:55:16.280 --> 00:55:17.940
Push. my lady.

950
00:55:18.010 --> 00:55:20.610
- Push! Push!

951
00:55:21.480 --> 00:55:22.640
Push!

952
00:55:22.750 --> 00:55:25.270
- You must push!

953
00:55:22.750 --> 00:55:25.270
Push!

954
00:55:27.250 --> 00:55:29.480
It needs to come now!

955
00:55:29.590 --> 00:55:30.780
Push!

956
00:55:32.830 --> 00:55:34.450
Push!

957
00:55:35.160 --> 00:55:37.320
You must push now. my lady!

958
00:55:38.430 --> 00:55:39.830
Push!

959
00:55:58.180 --> 00:56:00.180
I've reached the limit of my art.

960
00:56:02.050 --> 00:56:03.680
The child will not come.

961
00:56:06.460 --> 00:56:08.450
Ah. my brave girl.

962
00:56:13.900 --> 00:56:15.330
I am very sorry. my prince.

963
00:56:17.300 --> 00:56:19.290
We could lay open the womb...

964
00:56:20.310 --> 00:56:22.500
try to remove the infant

965
00:56:22.570 --> 00:56:24.200
by way of the blade.

966
00:56:25.480 --> 00:56:28.500
But I cannot say

967
00:56:25.480 --> 00:56:28.500
for a surety whether it lives.

968
00:56:28.580 --> 00:56:30.050
Would the mother survive it?

969
00:56:32.380 --> 00:56:33.370
No.

970
00:57:04.380 --> 00:57:06.580
Vhagar. dracarys.

971
00:57:11.920 --> 00:57:13.090
Dracarys!

972
00:57:15.760 --> 00:57:17.200
Dracarys!

973
00:57:21.770 --> 00:57:23.360
Dracarys.

974
00:57:24.140 --> 00:57:26.130
Dracarys!

975
00:57:28.270 --> 00:57:29.870
Dracarys.

976
00:57:50.430 --> 00:57:51.620
Laena!

977
00:58:14.590 --> 00:58:15.990
Be good to your mother. lads.

978
00:58:16.820 --> 00:58:18.450
I'll visit when I can.

979
00:58:21.930 --> 00:58:23.360
But that may be some time.

980
00:58:27.270 --> 00:58:28.260
Jace.

981
00:58:35.310 --> 00:58:36.710
I will return...

982
00:58:39.380 --> 00:58:40.810
I promise.

983
00:58:55.660 --> 00:58:59.620
I will be a stranger when we meet again.

984
00:59:16.520 --> 00:59:17.510
Princess.

985
00:59:39.910 --> 00:59:42.600
We will exchange letters by raven.

986
00:59:42.710 --> 00:59:46.340
- Won't that be fun?

987
00:59:42.710 --> 00:59:46.340
- Is Harwin Strong my father?

988
00:59:50.520 --> 00:59:51.880
Am I a bastard?

989
00:59:56.720 --> 00:59:58.250
You are a Targaryen.

990
01:00:00.260 --> 01:00:01.420
That's all that matters.

991
01:00:26.380 --> 01:00:27.410
A word?

992
01:00:34.430 --> 01:00:35.760
I take it he's gone.

993
01:00:38.330 --> 01:00:40.060
We're finished here. We're leaving.

994
01:00:43.070 --> 01:00:45.940
What of your offer? Jace and Helaena?

995
01:00:46.000 --> 01:00:47.770
I have been undermined...

996
01:00:48.640 --> 01:00:51.840
and made a spectacle.

997
01:00:48.640 --> 01:00:51.840
They whisper about me in the corridors.

998
01:00:51.940 --> 01:00:54.310
Well. I leave them to it.

999
01:00:58.280 --> 01:00:59.440
To Dragonstone then?

1000
01:01:00.490 --> 01:01:01.750
We should've left years ago.

1001
01:01:07.990 --> 01:01:09.790
What of your position?

1002
01:01:09.860 --> 01:01:12.190
You've always said

1003
01:01:09.860 --> 01:01:12.190
if you were absent from court.

1004
01:01:12.300 --> 01:01:15.200
she would pour her honey

1005
01:01:12.300 --> 01:01:15.200
in your father's ear.

1006
01:01:15.870 --> 01:01:19.030
The wise sailor

1007
01:01:15.870 --> 01:01:19.030
flees the storm as it gathers.

1008
01:01:21.310 --> 01:01:22.710
Laenor...

1009
01:01:24.480 --> 01:01:25.710
bring him.

1010
01:01:27.510 --> 01:01:29.640
We'll need every sword we can muster.

1011
01:02:46.190 --> 01:02:49.590
Fire! I will burn!

1012
01:02:49.690 --> 01:02:52.390
Harwin! Harwin!

1013
01:03:16.820 --> 01:03:20.450
What are children.

1014
01:03:16.820 --> 01:03:20.450
but a weakness?

1015
01:03:24.000 --> 01:03:25.620
A folly?

1016
01:03:26.800 --> 01:03:28.630
A futility?

1017
01:03:33.840 --> 01:03:36.000
Through them. you imagine you cheat

1018
01:03:36.110 --> 01:03:39.310
the great darkness of its victory.

1019
01:03:54.460 --> 01:03:59.450
You will persist forever.

1020
01:03:54.460 --> 01:03:59.450
in some form or another.

1021
01:04:02.270 --> 01:04:05.430
As if they will keep you

1022
01:04:02.270 --> 01:04:05.430
from the dust.

1023
01:04:16.480 --> 01:04:21.150
But for them.

1024
01:04:16.480 --> 01:04:21.150
you surrender what you should not.

1025
01:04:23.960 --> 01:04:27.720
You may know what is

1026
01:04:23.960 --> 01:04:27.720
the right thing to be done.

1027
01:04:27.830 --> 01:04:31.190
but love stays the hand.

1028
01:04:40.140 --> 01:04:41.330
Love...

1029
01:04:43.480 --> 01:04:45.470
is a downfall.

1030
01:04:50.420 --> 01:04:53.910
Best to make your way

1031
01:04:50.420 --> 01:04:53.910
through life unencumbered...

1032
01:04:55.520 --> 01:04:56.990
if you ask me.

1033
01:05:00.660 --> 01:05:01.920
They're dead.

1034
01:05:02.030 --> 01:05:05.020
You've heard the stories

1035
01:05:02.030 --> 01:05:05.020
of Harrenhal. Your Grace.

1036
01:05:06.730 --> 01:05:08.760
It was built in hubris

1037
01:05:06.730 --> 01:05:08.760
by Harren the Black

1038
01:05:08.870 --> 01:05:11.230
- as a monument to his own greatness.

1039
01:05:11.340 --> 01:05:14.330
Blood mixed into the mortar.

1040
01:05:16.510 --> 01:05:18.940
It is said to be a cursed place.

1041
01:05:19.610 --> 01:05:23.410
That it passes judgment

1042
01:05:19.610 --> 01:05:23.410
on all who pass beneath its gates.

1043
01:05:23.520 --> 01:05:25.110
You--

1044
01:05:25.220 --> 01:05:27.210
You passed judgment.

1045
01:05:28.850 --> 01:05:30.220
The Queen makes a wish.

1046
01:05:32.120 --> 01:05:35.790
What servant of the realm

1047
01:05:32.120 --> 01:05:35.790
would not strive to fulfill it?

1048
01:05:37.760 --> 01:05:41.390
I assume you will write

1049
01:05:37.760 --> 01:05:41.390
to your father now?

1050
01:05:43.370 --> 01:05:44.360
Larys...

1051
01:05:45.540 --> 01:05:47.770
I did not wish for this.

1052
01:05:49.970 --> 01:05:53.880
I feel certain you will reward me...

1053
01:05:55.650 --> 01:05:57.980
when the time is right.
